 <sect2 id='Win'>
     <title>Windows</title>
      <para>For using DocBook on Windows the most useful and easy program I found to use is:</para>
      <para>eDE - e-novative DocBook Environment <ulink url="http://www.e-novative-download.com/setup_eDE_1.2.0.exe"></ulink></para>
      <para>The documentation for this program can be found at <ulink url="http://www.e-novative-download.com/ede_chunk.zip"></ulink></para>
      <para><emphasis>You may need to change a few lines in the code to point to the DocBook stylesheets on your machine</emphasis></para>
  </sect2>
